Why these big Startups or Unicorns are not profitable to their investors, because their Strategy is wrong.

- Upfront service & added costs
- Minimum order rate
- Nested Pre-Order Feature
- Broad Rating Categorisation
- Grocery Stores being a filter rather than a feature (Swiggy Go)
